## Implementation Checklist

When adding a new SVG illustration:

- [ ] Remove any solid background rectangle (usually the first `<path>`)
- [ ] Replace all black/dark colors with `#4A2219`
- [ ] Replace cool grey/blue decorative elements with Clay tones
- [ ] Verify neon green (`#CCFF00`) is used for energy/highlight elements
- [ ] Ensure the SVG has no fixed width/height (use `viewBox` only)
- [ ] Test on dark background to ensure contrast

