## SwiftUI Integration

When displaying SVGs in SwiftUI:

```swift
SVGView(contentsOf: url)
    .aspectRatio(contentMode: .fit)
    .frame(maxWidth: .infinity)
    .frame(height: UIScreen.main.bounds.height * 0.42)
```

**Key points:**
- Use `maxWidth: .infinity` for full-width illustrations
- Use `aspectRatio(contentMode: .fit)` to maintain proportions
- Height should be ~40-45% of screen for onboarding illustrations

