## Future Color Updates

To update the color palette across all SVGs:

1. Update the hex values in this document
2. Use find/replace in each SVG file:
   ```
   Old: fill="#OLD_HEX"
   New: fill="#NEW_HEX"
   ```
3. Or create a build script that processes SVGs using this mapping

